*gnaws another enemy kneecap to shreds*<BR>Veloxia@hotmail.com<BR><img src="http://home.attbi.com/~2emiller/Sig4final.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umheddik.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mheddik</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 156<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(4/14/02 7:56:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=538.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: well...</span><hr size=1> I think it was very rude. First of all, at 51 he was obviously not there for experience, which means he was there for one of three reasons: 1) to PL an alt; 2) loot; 3) faction. If it was (1), then you can think of it as his other level=appropriate character was there, and you have no more right to the camp than he does. I consider #2 very doubtful. And #3 can be done in cooperative fashion. I've done that myself when I was bored, but I did it by buffing the people there, then debuffing the mobs for them to make them easier to kill (and thus getting me my faction hit).<br>
<br>
This server is no absolute haven from the inconsiderate. There are probably fewer such people here, but they certainly do exist, as you have seen. The good thing about this server is that reputation does mean something, and when people screw other people over, just spread the word. This may not have a tangible noticeable effect immediately, but over time it does make a difference.<br>
<br>
Coriolis, Sage of Erudin, Firiona Vie, Phantasmist<br>
